<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="extreme-adj">extreme <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'striːm/    美 /ɪk'striːm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>极度的</strong></h4>
<p>very great in degree：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>extreme cold / poverty
极其寒冷/赤贫</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>极端的；严重的</strong></h4>
<p>very unusual and severe or serious：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>extreme weather
极端天气</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>末端的；尽头的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the extreme north of China 
中国的最北端</p></div></div>